name: Haumea, at last! - Sun and her daughters 13
description: I was delighted to discover that when it came time to compose music for the 13th installment in this series, the dwarf planet, Haumea, was emitting strong Bossa cocktail jazz vibes with a bit of 808 kick thrown in. This is the final installment in a 13-song cycle in which I imagined an AI musician composing for an AI artist. Audio-responsive visuals by @johnowhitaker.
